6:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both AI Writer and ContentStudio share a solid foundation of core features including Api Access. Where AI Writer pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Long Form and Seo Tools, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, ContentStudio uniquely offers Short Form and Templates and Tone Control and Multilingual and Team Collaboration and Browser Extension, giving it an edge for users who prioritize these areas. \n\nLooking at user ratings, AI Writer holds an overall score of 5/10 and an ease of use score of 5/10, while ContentStudio scores 7/10 overall and 7/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, ContentStudio comes in at a lower starting price of $25/mo, while AI Writer begins at $29/mo. Neither platform offers a free plan, so you will need to budget for at least the starting tier from the beginning. Be sure to take advantage of any trial periods they may offer."}]]}]
